  <p><b><span id="Overview">Objective:</span></b> <span id="md-webpage-description" itemprop="description"><i>Information Security Management</i> aims to ensure the confidentiality, integrity and availability of an organization's information, data and IT services. ITIL Security Management usually forms part of an organizational approach to security management which has a wider scope than the IT Service Provider.</span></p>
